reviewText: Gratuitous T&A!  Death Metal!  Cheap Gore!  If the three aforementioned items excite you; then check it out!  I happen to like women of the 'Cornfed Dame' variety,and this film delivers the bologna and cheese, trailer trashed pulchritude I so love! Oh, and the death metal is ok, too!
This movie was home made, very "ship" Not worth my money. As I viewed the movie found out How bad it was.
